
Hi :)

The following is a list of the example animation scripts for use w/ Anitroll
and Pixcon.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------
			A N I M A T I O N S
--------------------------------------------------------------------------

---------
* earth *
---------

This directory contains files to generate an animation of a rotating/morphing
earth.

---------
* flock *
---------

This directory contains files to generate an animation involving a "flock
of birds" algorithm.

---------
* hla *
---------

This directory contains files to generate an animated logo.

-------
* run *
-------

This directory contains files to generate an animation through the cave
environement generated by a "SBFAST" primitive.  A version of this animation
was shown at SIGGRAPH `95 by Ken Musgrave, who came up w/ the initial
algorithm.

